<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ن ف خ:</span> <span class="c2">(نَفَخَ)</span> فِيهِ وَنَفَخَهُ أَيْضًا لُغَةٌ قَالَ الشَّاعِرُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلَا خُرَاسَانُ حَتَّى يُنْفَخَ الصُّورُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَبَابُهُ نَصَرَ،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَالَ:</span> أَجِدُ <span class="c2">(نُفْخَةً)</span> بِفَتْحِ النُّونِ وَضَمِّهَا وَكَسْرِهَا إِذَا <span class="c2">(انْتَفَخَ)</span> بَطْنُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>